<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #222; line-height: 1.7; }
  .letterhead { text-align: center; border-bottom: 3px solid #361963; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .company-name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #361963; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .company-address { font-size: 11px; color: #666; }
  .ref-line { font-size: 11px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .subject { font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: underline; }
  .content p { margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: justify; }
  .signature { margin-top: 60px; }
  .signature-line { border-top: 1px solid #333; width: 200px; margin-top: 50px; }
  table.details { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; }
  table.details td { padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
  table.details td:first-child { font-weight: bold; width: 40%; background: #f9f9f9; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="letterhead">
    <div class="company-name">{{companyLegalName}}</div>
    <div class="company-address">{{companyAddress}}</div>
    {{#if companyPan}}<div class="company-address">PAN: {{companyPan}} {{#if companyTan}}&nbsp;|&nbsp; TAN: {{companyTan}}{{/if}}</div>{{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="ref-line">Date: {{today}}</div>

  <div class="subject">TO WHOMSOEVER IT MAY CONCERN</div>

  <div class="subject">SALARY CERTIFICATE</div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>This is to certify that <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong> (Employee Code: {{employeeCode}}) is currently employed with <strong>{{companyLegalName}}</strong> as <strong>{{designation}}</strong> in the <strong>{{department}}</strong> department since <strong>{{formatDate dateOfJoining}}</strong>.</p>

    <p>The details of the current compensation are as follows:</p>

    <table class="details">
      <tr><td>Annual CTC (Cost to Company)</td><td>{{formatCurrency annualCTC}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Monthly Gross Salary</td><td>{{formatCurrency monthlyGross}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Employment Type</td><td>{{employmentType}}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <p>This certificate is issued on request of the employee for whatever purpose it may serve. It does not constitute a guarantee of continued employment.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature">
    <p>For <strong>{{companyLegalName}}</strong></p>
    <div class="signature-line"></div>
    <p>Authorized Signatory</p>
    <p>HR Department</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
